pted his new country and became one of the most noted and accomplished abstract sculptors of his time. In 1965, Villa <a href="https://artsandculture.google.com/entity/m04ztj">married</a> Claire Zafeirakou who was his companion until she passed away in November 2010. Edoardo Villa lived in <a href="https://artsandculture.google.com/entity/m0g284">Johannesburg</a> until his death on 1 May 2011.',
